## Installation üó≥

Clone repo github ini

```bash
git clone https://github.com/altamisatmaja/ads_km7_app.git
```

Masuk ke folder project

```bash
cd ads_km7_app
```

Install dependencies

```bash
flutter pub get
```

Jalankan

```bash
flutter run
```
